<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p><a href="">www.php.net/manual/en/mysqli.real-connect.php</a>" rel="nofollow"&gt;mysqli_real_connect() function has 8 parameters but {{Zend_Db_Adapter_Mysqli}} only uses 6 of them, letting down the {{$socket}} and {{$flags}} params.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
        $_isConnected = @mysqli_real_connect(
            $this-&gt;_connection,
            $this-&gt;_config['host'],
            $this-&gt;_config['username'],
            $this-&gt;_config['password'],
            $this-&gt;_config['dbname'],
            $port
        );
</code></pre>

<p>This blocks the user to use flags like {{MYSQLI_CLIENT_COMPRESS}} and {{MYSQLI_CLIENT_SSL}}.</p>

